additional_info:
**No claims are made about the quality of this code. I did the bare minimum amount of work needed to make the style usable.

<b>Single Column Mode can be enabled by adding the following styles after the main stylesheet:</b>

<pre>
/* Begin Single Column Settings: */
.index-row .post-tease {
  width: 100% !important;
  margin: 0 10px 0 0;
}
.index-row .post-tease > a {
  width: 280px;
  float: left;
}
.index-row .post-tease .post-meta {
  width: 550px;
  float: left;
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-left: 30px;
}
.index-row .comment-count {
  position: absolute;
  z-index: 3;
  bottom: 35px;
  left: 28.5%;
}
article.post-tease:after {
  width: 100%;
  margin-left: 0;
  border-left: none;
  border-right: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  display: none;
}

.post-tease .comment-count {
  text-shadow: -0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
  box-shadow: -1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
  bottom: initial;
  top:0;
  left: 250px;
  height: 30px;
  width: 40px !important;
  line-height: 31px;
}
.post-tease .comment-count.read {
  background: none #666 !important;
  color: #fff !important;
  text-shadow: none;
}
.post-tease .comment-count.unread {
  background: none #fa501e !important;
}

.post-tease .comment-count.unread:after {
  border-left: 5px solid #fa501e;
  border-top: 5px solid #fa501e;
}
.post-tease .comment-count.read:after {
  border-left: 5px solid #666;
  border-top: 5px solid #666;
}
.post-tease .comment-count:before,
.post-tease .comment-count:after {
	content: "";
  display: block;
  position: absolute;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  border: 5px solid transparent;
  position: absolute;
  right: 0px;
  top: 30px;
	left: initial;
}
.post-tease .comment-count:before {
  border-left: 5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  border-top: 5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  right: 1px;
  top: 30px;
}
/* End Single Column Settings */
</pre>

css:
@-moz-document domain('arstechnica.com'), domain('arstechnica.co.uk') {

body {
  background: black;
  color: #eee;
}
main {
  background: transparent;
}
.posts-column {
  background: #111;
  padding-left: 20px;
  padding-top: 20px;
}
.ad-row {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.ad-row + .content-row {
  margin-top: 0;
}
.ad-row + .content-row .posts-column {
  padding-top: 20px;
}
section.post-content {
  background: #111;
  padding-left: 240px;
  padding-right: 20px;
  margin-left: 0;
  margin-right: 0;
  width: 880px;
}
.comments-row #comments-area {
  background: #111;
  padding-left: 240px;
  padding-right: 20px;
  margin-left: 0;
  width: 880px;
  margin-top: 0;
}
.comments-row {
  margin-top: 0;
}
.comments-row #comments-area #comments {
  padding-top: 20px;
}
.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>header .author>a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #fa501e;
}


article.single .post-title {
  color: #fa501e;
}
article.single .post-lowerdek {
  color: #eee;
}

.post-tease:after {
  border: 2px solid #fa501e;
  border-top: none;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
  height: 15px;
  width: 60%;
  margin-left: 20%;
  bottom: 6px;
}

.post-tease .post-meta {
  background-image: none;
  background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.94);
}

.post-tease .post-meta h2 a {
  color: #fff;
}

.pullbox, .shortcode-img {
  background-color: transparent;
}
.shortcode-img figure img,
figure.intro-image img {
  mix-blend-mode: normal;
}
.post-tease figure div {
  background-color: #1a1a1a;
  background-blend-mode: normal;
}

figure.intro-image {
  background-color: transparent;
}

.single-row + .single-row {
  margin-top: 0;
}
.single-row + .single-row .post-content {
  padding-top: 20px;
}

figure.intro-image figcaption {
  background-color: transparent;
}
figure.intro-image figcaption,
.shortcode-caption {
  color: #aaa;
}

.lSSlideOuter .lSPager.lSGallery li.active, .lSSlideOuter .lSPager.lSGallery li {
  transition: border-radius .35s;
}

.shortcode-blockquote, .post-page blockquote {
  border: none;
  border-left: 10px solid #333;
  padding: 10px;
  padding-left: 20px;
}
.shortcode-blockquote .blockquote-content, .post-page blockquote .blockquote-content, .shortcode-blockquote .post-page blockquote p, .post-page blockquote .shortcode-blockquote p, .post-page blockquote p {
  color: #999;
}
#author-footer:before {
  content: ""; 
  border-top: 4px solid #fa501e;
  width: 60%;
  margin-left: 20%;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;

}
#author-footer {
  border-top: none;
  position: relative;
  padding-top: 20px;
}

.post-tease .post-meta h2 a:visited {
    color: #fdad80;
}

.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>header .icons .newbie-highlight,
.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>header .icons .controversial,
.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>header .icons .reader-fav {
  background-color: black;
}
.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>.body .quotetitle,
.comments-row #comments-area #comments>li>.body .quotecontent {
  border-color: #333;
  color: #999;
}
select, input, textarea {
  color: #333;
}

#recommendations-footer #sponsored-recommendations #outbrain-recs .outbrain-recommendation>a .ob-title {
  color: #eee; 
}

}
